<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2299] [EC2] mapreduce fixups for PE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2299</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Scripts as packaged need tweaks for PE to successfully complete in multiclient (map-reduce) mode. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
